data.title: Huntingdon College Magazine 2011-2012
data.meta_description: Huntingdon College Magazine 2011-2012 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides information about the Huntingdon Tomorrow capital campaign launched in 2011. The $16.5 million campaign aims to enhance facilities, academic programs, fine arts, athletics and increase enrollment. It will support the reintroduction of dance and theater majors, renovation of performance spaces, construction of a new dance studio and improvements to athletic facilities. The success of the campaign depends on support from alumni and donors to help Huntingdon College progress into an even more excellent future.
